OL,3,CIs Anas Sarwar moving to the Lords a u-
OL,4,Cturn?
OL,6,FITV Border's Political Reporter Oliver
OL,7,FWright looks at why Anas Sarwar
OL,8,Fswapping Scottish Labour Leadership
OL,9,Ffor the Lords might look like a u-turn
OL,10,Fon past principles:
OL,12,FJust when you thought the changes in
OL,13,Fleadership in the Labour party were
OL,14,Fdone - think again.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
