OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1784740728
OL,3,CIs Anas Sarwar moving to the Lords a u-
OL,4,Cturn?
OL,6,FLast night news broke that it is
OL,7,Fwidely understood Scottish Labour
OL,8,Fleader, Anas Sarwar, would step down
OL,9,Ffrom the top job - and from Holyrood -
OL,10,Fto take up a seat in the House of
OL,11,FLords and become a minister in Andy
OL,12,FBurnham's Government.
OL,14,FThe idea that Sarwar might ditch
OL,15,FHolyrood in favour of a peerage had
OL,16,Fbeen banded around over the last
OL,17,Fcouple of weeks by a few Labour
OL,18,Finsiders.
OL,20,FMost saw it as something that would
OL,21,Fnever happen.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
