PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1784740728
OL,3,CIs Anas Sarwar moving to the Lords a u-
OL,4,Cturn?
OL,6,FProbably because Anas Sarwar very
OL,7,Fpublicly called for the House of Lords
OL,8,Fto be scrapped - in 2022 he said it
OL,9,Fwas "an institution that has no place
OL,10,Fin 21st century politics."
OL,12,FAnd as recently as May, when asked if
OL,13,Fhe would ever take up a seat in the
OL,14,FLords the answer was an unequivocal
OL,15,F'no.'
OL,17,FThat has handed opposition parties of
OL,18,Fevery colour a bit of a gift.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
