PN,32304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1784740728
OL,3,CIs Anas Sarwar moving to the Lords a u-
OL,4,Cturn?
OL,6,FSarwar was the first senior Labour
OL,7,Fpolitician to call for Sir Keir
OL,8,FStarmer to step down as Prime
OL,9,FMinister. It was a slow process, but
OL,10,Fit marked the start of the tide
OL,11,Fturning against the man who won Labour
OL,12,Fa massive majority in the House of
OL,13,FCommons. But many within Labour also
OL,14,Fblame Starmer for the disastrous
OL,15,FHolyrood election results in May.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
