SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1784740728
OL,3,CIs Anas Sarwar moving to the Lords a u-
OL,4,Cturn?
OL,6,FA theme is developing around Andy
OL,7,FBurnham's ministerial appointments.
OL,8,FThose who were Starmer loyalists have
OL,9,Fbeen given the boot: Rachel Reeves,
OL,10,FDavid Lammy and Steve Reed to name but
OL,11,Fa few.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,324,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1784740728
OL,3,CIs Anas Sarwar moving to the Lords a u-
OL,4,Cturn?
OL,6,FAnd those who paved the way for
OL,7,FBurnham to get the top job seem to be
OL,8,Fsettling into shiny new offices in
OL,9,FWhitehall. John Healey, who stood down
OL,10,Fas Defence Secretary over funding has
OL,11,Fbeen made Chancellor. Miatta
OL,12,FFahnbulleh resigned and called for
OL,13,FStarmer to quit. She's now energy
OL,14,Fsecretary. And now Anas Sarwar is
OL,15,Fexpected to take up a role as a
OL,16,Fbusiness minister. You see where this
OL,17,Fis going.
OL,19,FAndy Burnham denies sowing division
OL,20,Fwithin his own party.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
